      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery out of corners. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, preserving the communicative steering rack that enthusiasts demand. While the finish shows minor signs of road use, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed in for the serious driver.",
